CUSTOMIZE: Character appearance editor

Syntax: customize

DESCRIPTION:
  Opens a menu to edit how your character appears to others:

    1. Description  - short text after your name on look
    2. Picture      - ASCII portrait (see: picture)
    3. Position     - use position and face commands
    4. Show summary - review current settings
    5. Done         - leave the menu

  The original game offered customize during and after creation.
  Use this any time to update your look.

SEE ALSO: describe, picture, position, face, look
